here the key intution is till is valid index
ans is
t.substr(0,valid_idx)+valid_elem+lowest possible permutation of remaining characters
so for every char we need to check whether a bigger element is present or not
if yes update the lastvalid index,if not check if current_elemnt is available if yes update current element
if current element is alos not present then that's it,we need to break and apply this
t.substr(0,valid_idx)+valid_elem+lowest possible permutation of remaining characters;
